**Default State**: Enabled for all apps.

Exact alarms expecting a
[`AlarmManager.OnAlarmListener`](https://developer.android.com/reference/android/app/AlarmManager.OnAlarmListener)
callback is dropped when the calling app goes into a cached
state.

To learn more about the changes to exact alarms in Android 14, see
[Schedule exact alarms are denied by default](https://developer.android.com/about/versions/14/changes/schedule-exact-alarms).

