3

Correct, baseline profiles are not used when running locally. It is possible to [manually side load](https://developer.android.com/topic/performance/baselineprofiles#measuring-baseline) one but using Macrobenchmark like you are doing is much easier.

P50 etc is a statistical distribution of your measured results. You can read it like

P90 means 90% of cases were measured to be better than this. Or inversely 10% of cases were worse.

